{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.2.1","label":"","reference":"Job 2:1","prev_osis_id":"Job.001.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.002.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-10: cf. Job 1:6, etc. (La 3:37, 38. 1 Pi 5:6.) Ap 2:10.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Job.2.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Or, les fils de Dieu vinrent un jour se pr\u00e9senter devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et Satan vint aussi au milieu d\u2019eux se pr\u00e9senter devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.2","name":"Job 2","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.2.2","name":"Job 2:2","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.1.22","name":"Job 1:22","id":"fra-LSG:Job.1.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.2.2","label":"","reference":"Job 2:2","prev_osis_id":"Job.002.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.002.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Job.2.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel dit \u00e0 Satan: D\u2019o\u00f9 viens-tu? Et Satan r\u00e9pondit \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel: De parcourir la terre et de m\u2019y promener.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.2","name":"Job 2","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.2.3","name":"Job 2:3","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.2.1","name":"Job 2:1","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.2.3","label":"","reference":"Job 2:3","prev_osis_id":"Job.002.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.002.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Job.2.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel dit \u00e0 Satan: As-tu remarqu\u00e9 mon serviteur Job? Il n\u2019y a personne comme lui sur la terre; c\u2019est un homme int\u00e8gre et droit, craignant Dieu, et se d\u00e9tournant du mal. Il demeure ferme dans son int\u00e9grit\u00e9, et tu m\u2019excites \u00e0 le perdre sans motif.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.2","name":"Job 2","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.2.4","name":"Job 2:4","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.2.2","name":"Job 2:2","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.2.4","label":"","reference":"Job 2:4","prev_osis_id":"Job.002.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.002.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Job.2.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Et Satan r\u00e9pondit \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel: Peau pour peau! Tout ce que poss\u00e8de un homme, il le donne pour sa vie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.2","name":"Job 2","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.2.5","name":"Job 2:5","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.2.3","name":"Job 2:3","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.2.5","label":"","reference":"Job 2:5","prev_osis_id":"Job.002.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.002.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Job.2.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Mais \u00e9tends ta main, touche \u00e0 ses os et \u00e0 sa chair, et je suis s\u00fbr qu\u2019il te maudit en face.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.2","name":"Job 2","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.2.6","name":"Job 2:6","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.2.4","name":"Job 2:4","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.2.6","label":"","reference":"Job 2:6","prev_osis_id":"Job.002.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.002.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Job.2.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel dit \u00e0 Satan: Voici, je te le livre: seulement, \u00e9pargne sa vie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.2","name":"Job 2","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.2.7","name":"Job 2:7","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.2.5","name":"Job 2:5","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.2.7","label":"","reference":"Job 2:7","prev_osis_id":"Job.002.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.002.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Job.2.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Et Satan se retira de devant la face de l\u2019\u00c9ternel. Puis il frappa Job d\u2019un ulc\u00e8re malin, depuis la plante du pied jusqu\u2019au sommet de la t\u00eate.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.2","name":"Job 2","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.2.8","name":"Job 2:8","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.2.6","name":"Job 2:6","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.2.8","label":"","reference":"Job 2:8","prev_osis_id":"Job.002.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.002.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Job.2.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Et Job prit un tesson pour se gratter et s\u2019assit sur la cendre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.2","name":"Job 2","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.2.9","name":"Job 2:9","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.2.7","name":"Job 2:7","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.2.9","label":"","reference":"Job 2:9","prev_osis_id":"Job.002.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.002.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Job.2.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Sa femme lui dit: Tu demeures ferme dans ton int\u00e9grit\u00e9! Maudis Dieu, et meurs!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.2","name":"Job 2","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.2.10","name":"Job 2:10","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.2.8","name":"Job 2:8","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.2.10","label":"","reference":"Job 2:10","prev_osis_id":"Job.002.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.002.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Job.2.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Mais Job lui r\u00e9pondit: Tu parles comme une femme insens\u00e9e. Quoi! Nous recevons de Dieu le bien, et nous ne recevrions pas aussi le mal!<\/p>\n<p class=\"p\">En tout cela Job ne p\u00e9cha point par ses l\u00e8vres.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.2","name":"Job 2","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.2.11","name":"Job 2:11","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.2.9","name":"Job 2:9","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.2.11","label":"","reference":"Job 2:11","prev_osis_id":"Job.002.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.002.012,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Visite de trois amis<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 11-13: cf. Ro 12:15. 1 Th 5:14. Job 6:14.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Job.2.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Trois amis de Job, \u00c9liphaz de Th\u00e9man, Bildad de Schuach, et Tsophar de Naama, apprirent tous les malheurs qui lui \u00e9taient arriv\u00e9s. Ils se concert\u00e8rent et partirent de chez eux pour aller le plaindre et le consoler!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.2","name":"Job 2","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.2.12","name":"Job 2:12","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.2.10","name":"Job 2:10","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.2.12","label":"","reference":"Job 2:12","prev_osis_id":"Job.002.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.002.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Job.2.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Ayant de loin port\u00e9 les regards sur lui, ils ne le reconnurent pas, et ils \u00e9lev\u00e8rent la voix et pleur\u00e8rent. Ils d\u00e9chir\u00e8rent leurs manteaux, et ils jet\u00e8rent de la poussi\u00e8re en l\u2019air au-dessus de leur t\u00eate.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.2","name":"Job 2","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.2.13","name":"Job 2:13","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.2.11","name":"Job 2:11","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Job.2.13","label":"","reference":"Job 2:13","prev_osis_id":"Job.002.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Job.003.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Job.2.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Et ils se tinrent assis \u00e0 terre aupr\u00e8s de lui sept jours et sept nuits, sans lui dire une parole, car ils voyaient combien sa douleur \u00e9tait grande.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Job.2","name":"Job 2","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.3.1","name":"Job 3:1","id":"fra-LSG:Job.3.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Job.2.12","name":"Job 2:12","id":"fra-LSG:Job.2.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb4b16be9.90988021');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb4b16be9.90988021\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb4b16be9.90988021","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb4b16be9.90988021'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb4b16be9.90988021\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}